{"tid":874493,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【二手成交】萬景峯兩房賣972萬 一周貴4.5%","createTime":"2018-10-24T08:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T11:49:29.000Z","uid":6211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6ea47d10af4fc5c7fbd9a65dcb5a8d3c919b1133","tid":874493,"uid":6211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:41:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181024/58830362\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181024%2F58830362&d=pHDFri3JC9cxyroEx5P5vGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=9d12e40b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181024%2F58830362&h=018d655c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181024/58830362</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181024/large/1540367350_dc72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181024%2Flarge%2F1540367350_dc72.jpg&h=69f48cdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中原地產陳文杰表示，荃灣指標屋苑萬景峯本月錄得約3宗成交，市場最新錄得2座低層D室成交，實用面積523方呎，兩房間隔，開價998萬元，減價26萬元，新近以972萬元沽出，呎價18,585元。<br />\n陳文杰指，原業主2011年以533萬元買入單位，持貨7年，賬面獲利439萬元或82%。本月中屋苑亦錄得另一宗兩房戶成交，6座低層G室，實用面積522方呎，成交價928萬元，呎價17,778元，是次新成交呎價對上一宗貴4.5%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/871637/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/871637/page/1</a><br />\n淡友J得兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d45ae8dc407746f1679141f2314f10b8686b455","tid":874493,"uid":58413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T11:49:29.000Z","msg":"呢單一定要計啦"}]}